      <title>英国央行称英国企业预计将在 2.5 年内至少提高价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/boe-says-uk-firms-expect-to-raise-prices-by-least-in-2-1-2-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国公司预计将把自己的价格提高到近 2.5 年来的最低水平，这进一步表明通胀压力的缓解势头正在增强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/boe-says-uk-firms-expect-to-raise-prices-by-least-in-2-1-2-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 08:47:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
